1. Definition
    #1.Be able to detect inputs
    #2.Require multiple input to pop the balloon
    #3.Utilise variables, conditions and functions

2. Design
    #Draw the Balloon
    #Check input is UP key pressed
    #Check condition, is balloon at MAX size
        #YES -> Clear balloon, write "POP!" -> END
        #NO -> Increase balloon size, return to draw balloon
    
    #PSEUDO CODE
    START
    
    Draw the balloon
    
    Has the key been pressed
        Has the balloon reached max size
            Clear the balloon
            Write "POP!"
    
        IF not
            Increase balloon size
            Draw Balloon
    
    END
    
